
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Convert HEX to RGB - GET (White)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=FFFFFF

### Convert HEX to RGB - GET (Red)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=FF0000

### Convert HEX to RGB - GET (Blue with #)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=#0000FF

### Convert HEX to RGB - GET (Shorthand)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=F0F

### Convert HEX to RGB - GET (Custom color)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=FF5733

### Convert HEX to RGB - POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hex": "FFA500"
}

### Test Error - Missing parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb

### Test Error - Invalid hex
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/convert/hex-to-rgb?hex=INVALID